"_blank&quot;">Kraemer and Kupfer (2006)</a>. Alternative approaches (comp.=
 Furukawa &amp; Leucht, 2011) allow to convert between d and NNT with a hig=
her precision and usually they lead to higher numbers. The Kraemer et al. (=
2006) approach therefore seems to probably overestimate the effect and it s=
eems to yield accurate results essentially, when normal distribution of the=
